## Update bucketlist [/bucketlists/3]

### Update bucketlist with id = 3 [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)
        
        {
            "name": "Feeding"
        }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 3,
            "name": "Feeding",
            "date_created": "2016-02-08 15:49:55",
            "date_modified": "2016-02-08 15:49:55",
            "user_id": 3
        }

