## Create new item [/bucketlists/4/items]

### Create item for bucketlist of id = 4 [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
        
        {
            "name": "Seed investment in a big company like Andela"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 13,
            "name": "Seed investment in a big company like Andel",
            "bucketlist_id": 4,
            "done": false,
            "date_created": "2016-02-08 15:49:55",
            "date_modified": "2016-02-08 15:49:55"
        }

